{"id": "1004144", "question": "matplotlib怎么画圆？", "description": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10\"><p>给定圆心和半径，matplotlib怎么画圆？</p></div>", "viewer": 7845, "tags": ["统计/机器学习", "数据可视化", "Python"], "answers": [{"lvl1_answer": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10 p-r\"><p><img data-filename=\"circle (1).png\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"width: 272px;\"/><br/></p><pre><code class=\"python\">import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\r\nplt.figure(figsize=(4, 4))\r\nplt.axis('equal')\r\nax = plt.gca()\r\nax.set_xlim((-2, 2))\r\nax.set_ylim((-2, 2))\r\ndisk1 = plt.Circle((0, 0), 1, color='r', fill=False)\r\nax.add_artist(disk1)\r\nplt.show()</code></pre></div>", "lvl2_answer": ["谢谢"]}]}